        "subject": "LU-868 Add early reply and netlatency into the timeout of waiting next replay.",
        "message": "LU-868 Add early reply and netlatency into the timeout of waiting next replay.\n\nDuring recovery, when setting the timeout for waiting the next replay, it should\nconsider netlatency(added into current timeout) and early reply as well, so if\nserver sends the early reply for the request, the client might extend the timeout\naccording to current estimate service time.\n\nChange-Id: I0d813caad935de6237d8d536970da5bada45704f\nSigned-off-by: wangdi <di.wang@whamcloud.com>\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
    }
